title: The TWO Programming Languages EVERY Beginner Should Start With (to learn how to code fast)

media:group.media:title: The TWO Programming Languages EVERY Beginner Should Start With (to learn how to code fast)
media:group.media:description:
It feels like every day there are more and more programming languages coming out. And while resources like YouTube and online courses exist, its really hard for new programmers to choose what language they should learn first when learning how to program. 

In this video, I'll suggest my two languages to learn how to program, and one method that I suggest to everyone to make sure they don't get discouraged along the way.
